text: As a person who has been running webcasts and virtual event for over ten years it never ceases to amaze me by some of the comments people make about technical issues.  99% issues you have on on your end.  It's either browser, bandwidth, computer, or user error.  As event professionals almost 2 years into this pandemic we need to learn this.
html: As a person who has been running webcasts and virtual event for over ten years it never ceases to amaze me by some of the comments people make about technical issues. 99% issues you have on on your end. It’s either browser, bandwidth, computer, or user error. As event professionals almost 2 years into this pandemic we need to learn this.
